Package ch.zhaw.spro.models

Klasse Shift

java.lang.Object
ch.zhaw.spro.models.Shift
public class Shift extends Object
Represents a shift in the scheduling system. It is used to model the details of a work shift including its date, time, type, and the associated employee.
